            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                        src="/works/br-wth.webp"
                        class="w-full"
                        alt="Local SEO improvement experts. We focus our organic marketing strategies, especially for small businesses, on fast local seo improvement. Reaching customers close to your business faster. Trust over 10 years experience in website design and over 6 years in digital marketing management experience for the best local seo strategies available on the Gold Coast. Highly recommended, 5 star, local SEO services."
                      />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadImg>

          <SectionHeadSecImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Boost Your Online Presence and Generate More Local Leads
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              The future of marketing.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              Local citations are references to your business information across the web. Consistency in these citations plays a significant role in local SEO. With meticulous local citation management, I ensure that your business information, such as your name, address, and phone number (NAP), is consistent across online directories and platforms. This not only boosts your local SEO but also establishes trust with search engines and potential customers. Link building is a crucial component of SEO, and this applies to local SEO as well. I'm well-versed in crafting effective local link building strategies that help your website gain authority in your target area. By acquiring high-quality backlinks from reputable local sources, we enhance your local search rankings, making your business more visible to local searchers.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                        src="/works/hero-estem.webp"
                        class="w-full"
                        alt="Local SEO is one of the biggest rising SEO factors. With Google Maps being used more and more for daily searches that blend in location data, it is clear that businesses need to be focusing on making sure they are always improving their local SEO rank, just to stay competitive. If you are a small brand trying to grow, serious effort and time should be put into Local SEO and Search Rank Optimisation"
                      />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadSecImg>

          <SectionHeadImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Localized Content That Speaks to Your Target Market
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              Convenient customer booking.
            </Fragment>
